text: haey nowpel del anak( mou ham meat) minban neamk dl puokke nouv ayeat namuoy noh puokke ban niyeay tha heto avei ban chea anak min bradit vea mk? chaur anak pol tha tampit khnhom thveuteam avei delke banhchouh mk aoy khnhom pi mcheasa robsakhnhom tebonnaoh . nih(kompir kuor an) kuchea phosdo tang teanglay mk pi mcheasa robsa puok anak ning chea kar changaoulobangheanh haeyning chea kar anet sraleanh samreab krom del mean chomnue
